info.description:
A PostgreSQL interface for Python.

This provides an interface to the libpq library.  It is not an DB API
library, but is instead designed to match the interface PostgreSQL
offers.

info.html_description:
A PostgreSQL interface for Python.

This provides an interface to the libpq library. It is not an DB API library, but is instead designed to match the interface PostgreSQL offers.
